Sentiment006.Factor_Description:
1.FF构建三因子;
2.个股收益与三因子回归,计算均衡收益U;
3.根据分析师一致预期各年末个股收益和年化增长率,计算未来1到10年的预期收益;
4.计算预期会计收益;
5.计算三阶段增长模型;
6.计算CFN;
7.Residual_Ret=RE-U-CF

TechIndex001.Factor_Description:
收集派发指标:将市场分为两股收集(买入)及派发(估出)的力量/
LC=REF(CLOSE,1);
DIF=CLOSE-IF(CLOSE>LC,MIN(LOW,LC),MAX(HIGH,LC));
ACD=SUM(IF(CLOSE=LC,0,DIF),0);
MAACD=EWA(ACD,N)

TechIndex002.Factor_Description:
动态买卖气指标:用开盘价的向上波动幅度和向下波动幅度的距离差值来描述人气高低的指标/
DTM=IF(O<=REF(O,1),0,MAX((H-O),(O-REF(O,1))));
DBM=IF(O>=REF(O,1),0,MAX((O-L),(O-REF(O,1))));
STM=SUM(DTM,P);
SBM=SUM(DBM,P);
ADTM=IF(STM>SBM,(STM-SBM)/STM,IF(STM=SBM,0,(STM-SBM)/SBM))

TechIndex004.Factor_Description:
AR指标是反映市场当前情况下多空双方力量发展对比的结果;
BR指标也是反映当前情况下多空双方力量争斗的结果/
AR=SUM(HIGH-OPEN,M)/SUM(OPEN-LOW,M)*100;
BR=SUM(MAX(0,HIGH-REF(CLOSE,1)),M)/SUM(MAX(0,REF(CLOSE,1)-LOW),M)*100

TechIndex005.Factor_Description:
变化率指数均值:股票的价格变化率RC指标的均值,用以判断前一段交易周期内股票的平均价格变化率/
RC=C/REF(C,m);
ARC=SMA(REF(RC,1),m,1)

TechIndex006.Factor_Description:
计算自价格达到近期最高值和最低值以来所经过的期间数,帮助投资者预测证券价格趋势、强弱以及趋势的反转等/
Aroon上升数=[(计算期天数-最高价后的天数)/计算期天数]*100;
Aroon下降数=[(计算期天数-最低价后的天数)/计算期天数]*100;
Aroon指标=Aroon上升数-Aroon下降数

TechIndex007.Factor_Description:
累计振动升降指标:以开盘、最高、最低、收盘价与前一交易日的各种价格相比较作为计算因子,研判市场的方向性/
LC=REF(C,1);
AA=ABS(H-LC);BB=ABS(L-LC);
CC=ABS(H-REF(L,1));
DD=ABS(LC-REF(O,1));
R=IF(AA>BBANDAA>CC,AA+BB/2+DD/4,IF(BB>CCANDBB>AA,BB+AA/2+DD/4,CC+DD/4));
X=(C-LC+(C-O)/2+LC-REF(O,1));
SI=16*X/R*MAX(AA,BB);
ASI=SUM(SI,0);
CUMASI=SUM(ASI,N)

TechIndex008.Factor_Description:
平均真实波幅:显示市场变化率的指标/
TR1=MAX(MAX((HIGH-LOW),ABS(REF(CLOSE,1)-HIGH)),ABS(REF(CLOSE,1)-LOW));
ATR=MA(TR1,m)

TechIndex011.Factor_Description:
顺势指标:测量股价是否已超出常态分布范围/
TYP=(HIGH+LOW+CLOSE)/3;
CCI=(TYP-MA(TYP,M))/(0.015*AVEDEV(TYP,M))

TechIndex012.Factor_Description:
佳庆指标:基于AD曲线的指数移动均线而计算得到/
AD=VOLx[(CLOSE-LOW)-(HIGH-CLOSE)]/(HIGH-LOW);
Chaikin_Oscillator=EMA(AD,10)-EMA(AD,3)

TechIndex014.Factor_Description:
钱德动量摆动指标/
CZ1=IF(CLOSE-REF(CLOSE,1)>0,CLOSE-REF(CLOSE,1),0);
CZ2=IF(CLOSE-REF(CLOSE,1)<0,ABS(CLOSE-REF(CLOSE,1)),0);
SU=SUM(CZ1,N);
SD=SUM(CZ2,N);
CMO=(SU-SD)/(SU+SD)*100

TechIndex015.Factor_Description:
估波指标:通过计算月度价格的变化速率的加权平均值来测量市场的动量,属于长线指标/
R(n1)=(CLOSE-REF(CLOSE,N1))/REF(CLOSE,N1)*100;
R(n2)=(CLOSE-REF(CLOSE,N2))/REF(CLOSE,N2)*100;
RC(n1,n2)=R(n1)+R(n2);
Coppock(n1,n2,n3)=WMA[RC(n1,n2),n3]

TechIndex017.Factor_Description:
异同离差乖离率:先计算乖离率BIAS,然后计算不同日的乖离率之间的离差,最后对离差进行指数移动平滑处理/
BIAS=(C-MA(C,P))/MA(C,P);
DIF=(BIAS-REF(BIAS,N));
DBCD=SMA(DIF,W,1)

TechIndex018.Factor_Description:
方向标准离差指数/
DMZ=IF((H+L)<=(REF(H,1)+REF(L,1)),0,MAX(ABS(H-REF(H,1)),ABS(L-REF(L,1))));
DMF=IF((H+L)>=(REF(H,1)+REF(L,1)),0,MAX(ABS(H-REF(H,1)),ABS(L-REF(L,1))));
DIZ=SUM(DMZ,N)/(SUM(DMZ,N)+SUM(DMF,N));
DIF=SUM(DMF,N)/(SUM(DMF,N)+SUM(DMZ,N));
DDI=DIZ-DIF

TechIndex026.Factor_Description:
成交量摆动指标:该指标在决定长期资金流量趋势的同时保持了对于短期资金流量的敏感性,因而可以用于预测短期价格拐点/
MeanPrice=AVERAGE(CLOSE+HIGH+LOW);
Volume_D=IF(MeanPrice>REF(MeanPrice,1),Volume,-Volume);
K1=EWA(Volume_D,34);
K2=EWA(Volume_D,55);
Klinger=EWA(K2-K1,6)
